synopsis: "Mstruct is a thin mutable layer on top of cstruct"
description: """
```ocaml
# #require "mstruct";;
# let b = Mstruct.create 9;;
val b : Mstruct.t = <abstr>
# Mstruct.set_string b "hello";;
- : unit = ()
# Mstruct.set_uint32 b 32l;;
- : unit = ()
```"""
